Creates a buffer based on the average square footage of a NYC block.

oz %>%
  filter(is.na(DESIGNATED)) %>%
  nrow() %>%
  equals(0) %>%
  stopifnot()

oz_proj <- oz %>%
  # project to nys plane in feet
  st_transform(2263)
oz_proj
oz_bound <- oz_proj %>%
  # we only want boundaries between selected and eligible tracts
  # need to filter that
  filter(DESIGNATED == "True") %>%
  st_union() %>%
  st_boundary()

oz_bound %>%
  st_union() %>%
  st_write("../00_data/oz_bound.geojson", delete_dsn = TRUE)
## Deleting source `../00_data/oz_bound.geojson' using driver `GeoJSON'
## Writing layer `oz_bound' to data source 
##   `../00_data/oz_bound.geojson' using driver `GeoJSON'
